Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:30.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「但我能領會到其聲音的含義」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:33.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣的肯定會催人淚下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:35.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您要養狗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:37.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬說她想養
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:40.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,哇  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:42.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為啥你們倆這麼高興
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:45.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因為  在姬去上學的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:47.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您肯定會把狗帶來這邊的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:49.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,獨自守家什麼的多可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:52.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,確實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:54.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不如說是有環境養狗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:57.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要養的話  請負起責任來養
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:01.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不要厭倦後就選擇置之不理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:02.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一直養到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:04.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,當然我是這麼打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:10.91,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H040404&\frz311.7\move(1152,298,1236,150,0,5735)}周刊少年  漫畫人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:10.91,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：作者名源自漫畫家江口壽史
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:10.91,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\shad3\c&H1200A9&\frz38.65\3c&HDDDCDF&\move(1168,698,1252,548,0,5735)}新連載!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:10.91,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\shad4\c&HDDDCDF&\3c&H3E354F&\frz37.42\4c&H40354E&\move(1124,938,1210,788,0,5735)}「白色鱷魚」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:10.91,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：白色鱷魚本是流傳在美國的一個都市傳說又名「下水道的鱷魚」  這兒是指江口壽史在漫畫截稿日逼近時產生幻覺把白紙看成鱷魚的捏他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:10.91,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fs52\shad1\c&H23DCE7&\3c&H2A445D&\frz39.45\move(1336,924,1414,774,0,5735)}第一回
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:10.91,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fs35\frz39.26\c&H1328B8&\3c&H1CE1EA&\move(1350,784,1430,638,0,5735)}大容量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:10.91,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\c&H7D2C44&\frz39.26\move(1430,834,1514,686,0,5735)}60{\fs40}P
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:10.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,總覺得  養狗和開新連載挺像的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:15.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一開始挺好的  但要長久堅持就很難
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:17.05,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fs45\frz270\pos(524,144)}多久才會恢復連載啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:19.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,以及  要讓其結束更是難上加難
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:23.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,確實  一旦開始了就得照顧到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:25.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,正因為如此我是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:29.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在未完結的作品裡  沒有名作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:35.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不管人氣有多高  半途而廢的漫畫不管哪個都是垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:36.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說過頭了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:42.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,與之相比  我有著讓五部連載作品完結了的傲人戰績
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:46.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,雖然在這之中有三個都是短命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:47.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,別說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.95,0:03:53.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「漫畫家只能幹十年左右」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:56.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「所以請儘可能地對他們好點」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:58.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,啥玩意  這是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:01.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,漫畫家的十誡  我試著做出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:03.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「請給漫畫家寄信」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:07.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「因為沒有反饋而不安  他們會淚如雨下」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:13.73,kakushigoto in 11,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\bord0\pos(646,14)}漫畫家和讀者的10個約定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:13.73,kakushigoto in 11,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\bord6\pos(264,254)}1.  漫畫家只能幹十年左右。所以請儘可能地對他們好點。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:13.73,kakushigoto in 11,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\bord6\pos(264,328)}2.  請不要跳著看漫畫。光是這樣就很感謝了。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:13.73,kakushigoto in 11,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\bord6\pos(266,402)}3.  請耐心地追連載。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:13.73,kakushigoto in 11,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\bord6\pos(264,476)}4.  請不要忘記漫畫家也是人。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:13.73,kakushigoto in 11,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\bord6\pos(266,548)}5.  突然改變漫畫路線是有理由的。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:13.73,kakushigoto in 11,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\bord6\pos(266,624)}6.  請給漫畫家寄信。因為沒有反饋而不安，他們會淚如雨下。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:13.73,kakushigoto in 11,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\bord6\pos(268,694)}7.  請不要罵漫畫家。大家都經不起罵。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:13.73,kakushigoto in 11,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\bord6\pos(268,768)}8.  連載作品長篇化了也請讀下去。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:13.73,kakushigoto in 11,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\bord6\pos(264,838)}9.  你還有其他的漫畫可以看，但我只能畫這一個。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:13.73,kakushigoto in 11,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\bord6\pos(246,918)}10.  請讀到最終回。並且銘記它。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:09.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不妙  要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:10.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太單方面了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:12.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以老師  狗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:15.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎  怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:24.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,後藤老師  您在休息麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.65,0:04:25.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一子老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:28.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您有在養狗麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:30.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,已經是條老狗了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:34.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我初中的時候  無論如何都想養就買來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:38.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因為一個人在家的時候很多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:40.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可以說我是被這孩子所拯救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:43.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:46.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬也  沒有兄弟姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:52.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:57.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬  要負起責任來養哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:04:59.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可以麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:02.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要像對弟弟妹妹一樣的愛護哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:06.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,最喜歡爸爸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:12.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊  小姬想養狗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:13.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:16.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,會變得熱鬧起來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:18.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,話說  這位是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:21.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:24.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原來不是獨生子女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:27.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我有說過我是獨生子女麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:33.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,最近  有傳言說一子老師在和某人幽會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:34.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真假？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:35.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:37.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,終於有男朋友了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:39.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這件事有必要開個會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:41.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畢竟是一子老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:44.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,肯定是被人騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:46.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,偵探團出動了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:49.57,kakushigoto in 10,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\bord2\move(1068,428,1068,664,2027,2236)}會議中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:49.57,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\bord2\frz263.4\move(606,422,606,654,2027,2236)}目黑川  偵探事務所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:49.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是不是壞男人必須得調查下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:52.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,傳言說是在遛狗的途中幽會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:54.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那就是公園了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:55.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,走起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:58.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:01.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小孩子大都喜歡狗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:03.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,狗狗會教人各種各樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:07.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對於情操教育似乎也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:09.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:14.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那倆孩子  每次我遛狗都會過來摸摸狗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:17.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那真是辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:18.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,等等哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:22.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這麼容易吸引小孩過來  不是很危險嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:24.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:25.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:28.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,咦  是小姬的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:30.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,穿得好像漫畫家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:32.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬的爸爸是漫畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:34.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬的爸爸是漫畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:37.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,暴露的可能性不是變高了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:37.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:41.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師  請聽我一言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:44.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說曹操曹操到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:46.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我看見了哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:49.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這隻狗狗是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:50.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:55.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}乖乖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:59.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,咦  沒和誰在一起麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:00.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:02.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師以外還有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:06.78,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\pos(840,350)}養狗的家常便飯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:06.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,遛狗時  人們眼中只有狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:10.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在旁邊的人基本上就跟空氣沒區別
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:10.24,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(1110,140)\c&H213859&}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:13.78,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\c&H141A2B&\pos(808,68)}無視
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:13.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,飼主的面孔也不會被記住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:16.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,雖然幫大忙了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:18.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但總感覺心情複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:23.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你好  關於募集領養這件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:32.80,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord5\c&HF0F6F7&\3c&HD4DD94&\frz328.5\frx24\fry10\org(1485.6,265.6)\pos(1313.6,264)}送狗崽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:32.80,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\frz331.9\frx12\fry6\org(1434,516.8)\pos(920.8,562.4)}狗媽媽生了好多可愛的狗崽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:32.80,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs40\frx8\fry2\c&H4D5D71&\pos(263.6,996)\org(978.8,1047.2)\frz331.5}能把小狗當成家庭成員好好對待的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:32.80,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs40\frz330.5\frx8\fry2\c&H4D5D71&\org(1149.2,1233.2)\pos(434,1182)}請致電
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:28.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對不起  全部都已經定下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:29.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:32.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒事  謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:37.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,稍微  放下心來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:42.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.81,0:07:46.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:49.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這是遛狗的訓練哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:51.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為了不被狗狗拉著跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:55.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是為了不被狗狗拉著跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:58.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,更重要的是教會狗狗不要拉著人跑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:00.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:03.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,話說剛剛有什麼話想說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:04.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:06.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:11.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你  你們在幹什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:14.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,肯定是在做迎接小狗的準備啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:15.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是  還沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:17.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不管什麼事準備工作都很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:20.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什麼時候會來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:23.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其  其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:27.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.06,0:08:30.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是說好要養的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:33.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為啥你們會這麼悲傷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:36.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,特別是你  那個時候不是不在場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:38.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,芥子是之後聽到這件事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:40.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他是我們之中最期待的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:45.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,連這些傢伙都變成這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:50.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,結果到最後還是我們在照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:54.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,丈夫去公司  孩子去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:57.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒個老婆在家的話是養不了狗的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:04.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:07.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:09.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:11.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,歡迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:17.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,關於小狗  說是找到了新家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:21.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:25.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,週末去寵物店看看其他的小狗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:25.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:29.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然我們家養不了狗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:32.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畢竟只有爸爸和我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:35.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在這家裡養狗的話狗狗會很可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:38.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以  這樣反而更好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:40.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:44.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能…養不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:47.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,即便是我們家也是可以養狗的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:52.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我們也是能養狗的  普通家庭！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:57.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,又是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:03.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這是第三代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:08.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,難得都準備了  狗卻不來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:11.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,至少出於安慰  把這幅畫裝飾起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:16.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,狗狗和…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:18.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:19.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這幅畫是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:23.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在這之前我去鎌倉放原稿的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:27.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在倉庫的角落找到了個鋪滿灰塵的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:30.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師也能畫這種畫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:33.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,日本畫吧  這是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:35.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這筆觸  好像在哪兒見過的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:38.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這是最近畫的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:41.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,署名日期寫錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:46.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:48.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.79,0:10:55.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這孩子是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:57.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬說養不了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:10:58.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那就爸爸一人來養囉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:01.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不  不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:03.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,只讓爸爸一個人養  我也來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:05.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,該怎麼辦好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:08.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是吧  第四代
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:09.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,第四代？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:18.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬  會感冒的上床和爸爸一起睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:20.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我要在這兒和狗狗一起睡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:23.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,狗狗也帶回來了  好啦聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:25.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我睡覺翻身會打到人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:36.34,kakushigoto in 11,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,0)\bord0\fs60\pos(704,172)}爸爸與女兒的10個約定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:31.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「爸爸只能陪女兒一起睡到十歲左右」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:36.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「所以睡的時候請儘可能的黏著爸爸」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:47.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:52.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:58.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:01.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師  這隻小狗的名字叫什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.44,0:12:02.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我還沒想好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:05.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不快點給它取個名字也太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:06.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我來給它取名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:08.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為什麼你來取啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:08.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:12.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這幅畫  是誰帶到這裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:17.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也沒必要這麼責備我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:19.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是亂搞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:21.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這不挺好的一幅畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:23.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬畫得這麼可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:25.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原來老師您也會畫這樣的畫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:29.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這幅畫中的少女並不是姬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:31.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,誒  那是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:38.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這是  姬的媽媽小時候的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.44,0:12:42.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畫這幅畫的人則是她的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:45.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬的媽媽小時候的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:47.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:49.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬的爺爺…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:50.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那不就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:53.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,然後  同在這幅畫上的狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:55.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,則是這傢伙的祖先
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:57.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,從畫上的狗狗數起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:58.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,它已經是第四代了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:01.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,母親養的狗狗的子孫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:04.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,歷經千萬山水來到了女兒的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:08.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,感覺就像是已注定好的家譜一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:09.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,雖然很不甘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:11.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但這的確是一幅不錯的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:15.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,雖然作者就是個垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:16.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你說對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:18.60,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\frz334\pos(1001.6,596.8)}母女的繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:22.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,家譜啊  漫畫家之中好像也有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:25.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就像誰是誰的助手那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:26.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是在師傅手下幹的時間長了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:28.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,自己的畫就和師傅的有些像了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:32.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以也就能夠知道這人是誰的助手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:35.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你看那不懂行的人又在胡說些什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:37.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:39.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不就是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:43.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,並不是助手的畫像師傅的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:45.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而是那是助手自己本身的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:46.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我根本聽不懂你在說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:50.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你的意思是老師不畫了全都助手畫是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:51.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,並不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:53.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:55.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,會有些「風格」上相像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:56.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,風格？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:13:59.65,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\frz270\c&H1E1F23&\pos(272,142.4)}髮色光澤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:13:59.65,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\frz270\c&H1E1F23&\pos(622.4,144)}網點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:59.65,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\frz270\c&H1E1F23&\pos(969.6,150.4)}效果線
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:59.65,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\frz270\c&H1E1F23&\pos(1358.4,153.6)}路人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:13:59.65,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\frz270\c&H1E1F23&\pos(1748.8,156.8)}背景
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:58.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,既然涉及到眾多的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:02.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那麼恐怕原稿的十分之七都出自於助手之手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:04.78,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\fs45\c&H3FDBF4&\3c&H1E1F23&\pos(204.8,944)}助手畫的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:04.78,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1300,0)\bord4\fs45\c&H3FDBF4&\3c&H1E1F23&\pos(878.4,945.6)}完成的原稿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:04.78,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\fs45\c&H3FDBF4&\3c&H1E1F23&\pos(1512,940.8)}老師畫的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:04.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:06.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果按照自己工作時的畫法畫下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.69,0:14:08.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,自己的畫風也會同化成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:12.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是…這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:13.91,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}失望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:13.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看上去你很不情願嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:15.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒有  沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:17.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你也不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:20.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也就是最開始相似  等過幾年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:24.96,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\shad4\c&H6C703D&\4c&HA8BA8A&\pos(446.4,49.6)}助手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.58,0:14:24.96,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\frz270\c&H445168&\pos(633.6,526.4)}進步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:24.96,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\shad4\c&H6C703D&\4c&HA8BA8A&\pos(1289.6,51.2)}老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.58,0:14:24.96,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\frz270\c&H4A5263&\pos(1340.8,529.6)}退步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:24.96,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\c&H495C70&\frz308\pos(875.2,526.4)}不同水平
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:23.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,師傅的畫就會變差
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:24.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,弟子的畫就變好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:26.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對  對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.71,0:14:27.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你說誰會變差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:29.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我說的…是一般論
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:31.89,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord5\c&HBAA78F&\3c&HCEF2F9&\pos(1356.8,582.4)}搬運{\c&HD0CAB9&}鋼琴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:34.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這是…怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:37.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,感覺好厲害啊  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:40.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,又是那傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:43.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:46.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那麼大的東西對我們家裡來說只是個麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:48.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那是和狗一對兒的遺產
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:50.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,遺產？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:53.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,她一定和她母親同樣擁有著才能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:56.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,給她找個好老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:01.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是的  多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:12.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好…可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:15.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這人已經是暢銷新人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:17.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這人好像曾是老師的助手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:20.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就那個JUMP的新人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:24.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這人的畫風不跟老師您一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.85,0:15:24.44,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\c&H40494C&\3c&HC0DDD9&\frz15.39\pos(537.6,200)}人氣{\bord3\c&HC1DEDA&\3c&H3F4A4D&}大爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.85,0:15:24.44,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\frz5.201\c&H434C4F&\3c&HC2DEDA&\pos(388.8,438.4)}充實海鮮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:26.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒印象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:27.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這好像還是他的真名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:31.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,偶爾也會有不是我助手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:34.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但畫風和我一樣的新人出現
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:36.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,喜歡到了極點自然也就會像的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:40.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但也沒必要模仿老師您吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:41.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這其中肯定有的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:43.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就算不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:44.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在接受責編指導時
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:46.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這些是最近的暢銷作家的畫 你就照著這個畫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:47.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也會有責編這樣對新人說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.33,0:15:48.46,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\c&H797F8B&\pos(1816,99.2)}最近的流行趨勢就是這種感覺的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:48.46,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\c&H797F8B&\pos(763.2,212.8)}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:51.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,暢銷作家…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:58.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我原本也以為是從咱們這裡出道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.31,0:16:00.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畢竟畫風這麼相似
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:02.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也許當過一回這裡的短期助手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:05.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,短期…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:10.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:13.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:15.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,後藤老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:17.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這就是上次您說的小狗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:20.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:22.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其實  突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:25.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,出現了個和自己特別像的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:29.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您…您有頭緒嗎  對方是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:31.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:33.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:35.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,和我幹過一次的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:38.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這這這…這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:41.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,名字可能不記得但至少長相是記得的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:42.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,長相嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:46.60,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(440,500)\c&H4F5153&\frz39.91\pos(163.2,417.6)}原稿我已經確認完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:46.60,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(440,500)\c&H2B5035&\frz39.91\pos(816,403.2)}18頁第三個格子的背景就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:46.60,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(440,500)\c&H4F5153&\frz39.91\pos(664,937.6)}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:46.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,確實  現在都是網絡社會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:48.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果是宅在家裡的網絡助手的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:50.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也會有不知道長相的這種情況發生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:53.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也許是在網上認識和我幹過一次的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:56.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我好受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:17:00.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:04.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原來是說的助手的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:06.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那你以為是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:07.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:12.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我想那人應該是喜歡老師的畫才比較像的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:13.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你也這麼認為?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:17.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不也有狗狗會和主人比較像的這種說法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:18.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但也有相反的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:20.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,主人會和狗狗相像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:21.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太過於喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:24.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,到最後大家都會變得和自己喜歡的東西相似
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:29.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可能我也會太過於喜歡石原里美最後…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:30.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太過於喜歡…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:36.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,和喜歡的東西變得相似
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:40.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:44.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬也會變得像我一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:50.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,先變得和爸爸一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:51.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你指的是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:54.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:58.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然他不是喜歡老師的作品才模仿的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:02.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我向集英社的熟人問過了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:05.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說是提了要求說模仿後藤老師的畫風
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:08.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然是接受了責編指導啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:10.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不愧是JUMP  有眼光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:15.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,並不是  好像本來說的是另外一個後藤老師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:18.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是那個賣得比較好的後藤老師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:21.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說是沒有重畫的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:22.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就這麼刊登上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:24.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,更諷刺的是這作品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:26.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不知道為什麼還挺受腐女喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:30.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,青出於藍勝於藍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:32.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,才沒有勝過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:34.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不過竟然受女生喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.25,0:18:37.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我看著好像和我的沒什麼差別
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:38.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,難道這其中有些微妙的區別嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.51,0:18:43.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為什麼您一臉坦然地開始參考那部作品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:45.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您沒點職業尊嚴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:47.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這不常有的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:50.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,作品動漫化後  覺得那樣的角色更帥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.39,0:18:52.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,於是就將原作畫風偏向了動畫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:55.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,青出於藍勝於藍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:57.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,藍便把青抄個遍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.44,0:19:01.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,從來們聽說過這麼噁心人的諺語
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:03.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,話說回來  十丸院
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:05.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我叫你找的新人助手你給我找來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:06.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,得趕緊增加點人手了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:09.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果您不介意聽的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.16,0:19:12.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我問了很多編輯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:13.08,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\frz270\c&H4F5C6C&\3c&HEDEFEF&\pos(1332.8,216)}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:16.30,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\bord2\frz270\c&H4F5C6C&\3c&HEDEFEF&\pos(902.4,220.8)}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:15.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大家都說不想把自己手上未來可期的新人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:19.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,放到後藤老師您這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:22.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就因為害怕染上愛寫黃段子這一原因嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:24.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也有這個原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:29.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但主要原因好像還是不想將新人放到出道機率比較低的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:32.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還不是因為你們一直沒出道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:33.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這怪我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:36.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,後藤工作室不像不二多工作室那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:40.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有著代代相傳輝煌的家譜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:41.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你們聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:46.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所有人  給我半年之內出道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:48.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:51.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:55.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能不能等我培養好有希望的新人之後你們再出道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.33,0:19:58.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但這又需要自己助手出道的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:00.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是進退兩難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:04.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就當是人氣作家都是從我的工作室出來的不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:06.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您打算是虛報自己的漫畫履歷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:11.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就算是跟了個多好的師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:13.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能夠出道與否還不是得靠自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:20.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我在上鋼琴課
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:22.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這…這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:25.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我介紹這個人來這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:25.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:27.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你別看他雖然是這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:29.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是馬莉歐先生他可是很有才能的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:32.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,居然誇讚我是這個樣子  我真是高興
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:34.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這…這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:36.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我一天就學會了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:38.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:39.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,會沾染上變態病毒的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:40.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,滾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:48.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然得讓姬跟個好老師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:51.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這是姬做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.35,0:20:54.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,雖然是納德拉小姐守著我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.81,0:20:56.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但全都是我親手做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:21:00.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真好吃…而且這味道很熟悉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:01.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我都是按照菜譜上做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:04.15,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\bord3\frz18.85\c&H54DDF6&\3c&H2263DA&\frx6\fry4\pos(1160,712)}菜譜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:03.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,放在那個箱子裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.36,0:21:10.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這也是代代相傳的家譜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:11.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:12.91,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\bord4\c&HE8C486&\3c&HA98545&\frz281.4\pos(1078.4,422.4)}淚目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.24,0:21:14.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那是  狗狗吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:24.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬她沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:26.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,肯定沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.13,0:21:28.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嘴上這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.64,0:21:31.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但提議一起悄悄跟著來的不就是霧子你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:33.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,話是這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:38.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你們  一起約好來開同學聚會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:41.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那可得叫上我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.69,0:21:45.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一…一子老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:48.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您居…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.53,0:21:49.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,居然沒穿運動衫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.74,0:21:50.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你們意外這個啊
